  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Children with refractory epilepsy who are candidates for a treatment with vagus nerve
      stimulation will be prospectively randomized into 2 arms. Vagus nerve stimulation parameters
      are programmed and adjusted during outpatient clinic visits, within the normal clinical
      practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
